ast.name: Math Mage
ast.comment:
Math Mage is an educational game with fruit ninja style gameplay that tests students knowledge of odd, even, prime and times tables (multiples of) from 3 up to 12.

Game Design and Coding: David Renton
Blog: games4learning.co.uk
Twitter: @drenton72
Email: drenton@reidkerr.ac.uk

Lead Artist: Michael Philip
Blog: micgrol.deviantart.com

Animation: Donny Nguyen
Blog: mrbubblewand.wordpress.com

Sound Effects: Mike Koenig soundbible.com and www.SoundJay.com

Audio Samples: Lochfield Primary School

#PILAppathon
